PTX Fence-SC-Weak
"Figure 6 of https://dl.acm.org/doi/epdf/10.1145/3297858.3304043"
{
x=0;
y=0;
P0:r0=0;
P1:r1=0;
}
 P0@cta 0,gpu 0         | P1@cta 1,gpu 0         ;
 st.weak x, 1           | st.weak y, 1           ;
 fence.sc.gpu           | fence.sc.gpu           ;
 ld.weak r0, y          | ld.weak r1, x          ;
~exists
(P0:r0 == 0 /\ P1:r1 == 0)